beatleader-is-an-open-source-leaderboard.origin:
BeatLeader is an open-source leaderboard system for the Beat Saber. Our goal is to make an expandable, sustainable, and transparent system
			with zero bus factor and reliance on a specific person.
beatleader-is-an-open-source-leaderboard.translated:
BeatLeader是一个针对Beat Saber的开源排行榜系统。我们的目标是打造一个可扩展、可持续、透明的系统，
			并且不依赖于任何个人。

mods-are-posting-replays-to-the-server-t.origin:
Mods are posting replays to the server, the website is showing leaderboards and cool stats. Replay viewers can show plays on all platforms
			for every score. You can even draft the web battle royale of replays. Maps are ranked every week after map voting and criteria check.
mods-are-posting-replays-to-the-server-t.translated: Mods正在将回放上传到服务器，网站正在显示排行榜和酷炫的统计数据。回放观看者可以在所有平台上显示每个分数的播放情况。你甚至可以使用回放创建网页版战斗皇家。地图每周根据地图投票和标准检查进行排名。

not-a-lot-actually-the-core-part-of-the-.origin:
Not a lot, actually. The core part of the BeatLeader is done, even the server is more or less sustainable. But we have a lot of plans for
			future features.
not-a-lot-actually-the-core-part-of-the-.translated: 实际上还没做很多。 BeatLeader的核心部分已经完成，甚至服务器也比较可持续。但我们对未来的功能有很多计划。

how-this-is-different-from-the-scoresabe.origin: How this is different from the ScoreSaber

the-main-difference-is-that-all-our-proj.origin:
The main difference is that all our projects are open-source. And this is part of the reason why they exist. That's it. :coffage: We are
			doing our best to make it cooler, with more features, integrations, customization, etc... But the main goal was to make it transparent
			and expandable by anyone.
the-main-difference-is-that-all-our-proj.translated: 主要的区别在于我们所有的项目都是开源的。这也是它们存在的部分原因。就是这样。 ：coffage: 我们正尽力使它更酷，具备更多功能、集成和定制等... 但主要目标是让任何人都可以透明地扩展它。

you-can-find-links-to-github-in-the-foot.origin:
You can find links to GitHub in the footer. Check our Discord server for instructions on how to start making changes. Pull requests are
			welcome! But you don't need to be a developer to help. We need a lot of help with design, ranking maps, drawings, events, etc... Feedback,
			crash reports and your wildest ideas are great too!
you-can-find-links-to-github-in-the-foot.translated: 你可以在页脚找到链接到GitHub的地址。请查看我们Discord服务器上的说明以了解如何开始进行更改。我们欢迎Pull requests！但你不需要成为开发人员来提供帮助。我们需要很多设计、排名地图、绘图、活动等方面的帮助...反馈、崩溃报告和你最疯狂的想法也是很好的！

replays-may-contain-personally-identifia.origin:

		identifiable information. Example being your movements, height or even your body shape. Your data, including associated personally
		identifiable information, will be broadly publicly available to anyone with an internet connection via the BeatLeader website. It will
		also be accessible to academic researchers, who may use it to conduct research topics such as VR security, privacy, and usability.

2023-census-of-beat-saber-users:f.translated: 2023 年 Beat Saber 用户普查

your-responses-will-have-a-meaningful-im.origin:
Your responses will have a meaningful impact on the Beat Saber modding community, in addition to advancing public knowledge on
			safety, usability, and data security/privacy in VR.
your-responses-will-have-a-meaningful-im.translated: 您的回答对于Beat Saber的修改社区有重要影响，同时也推动了VR领域的安全性、可用性以及数据安全/隐私方面的公众知识。

beatleader-together-with-university-of-c.origin:
BeatLeader together with University of California, Berkeley conducted a large-scale comprehensive survey of 1,006 Beat Saber players
			that sheds light on several important aspects of playerbase, including their background, biometrics, demographics, health information,
			behavioral patterns, and technical device specifications. This further provide insights into the ranking community and potential
			correlation with player performance.
beatleader-together-with-university-of-c.translated: BeatLeader与加利福尼亚大学伯克利分校合作进行了一项规模庞大的综合调查，共有1,006名Beat Saber玩家参与，揭示了玩家群体的多个重要方面，包括他们的背景、生理数据、人口统计信息、健康状况、行为模式和设备技术规格。这进一步提供了对排名社区和与玩家表现的潜在相关性的见解。

the-survey-was-conducted-among-ranked-pl.origin:
The survey was conducted among ranked players, and the results might not be representative of all Beat Saber players. Additionally,
			the survey relied on self-reported data, which can be subject to bias. And correlation does not imply causation, so these findings
			should be interpreted with caution.
the-survey-was-conducted-among-ranked-pl.translated: 此调查针对排名玩家进行，结果可能不能代表所有Beat Saber玩家。此外，调查依赖于自我报告的数据，可能存在偏见。而相关性并不意味着因果关系，因此应谨慎解读这些发现。

younger-players-outperform-older-players.origin:
Younger players outperform older players on average, with 18-19 being the best performing age group. Possible explanations
				include a reduction with age of eyesight, reaction time, physical fitness, and neuroplasticity.
younger-players-outperform-older-players.translated: 年纪较小的玩家平均表现优于年纪较大的玩家，其中18-19岁年龄组的表现最好。可能的解释包括随着年龄增长，视力、反应时间、体能和神经可塑性的减少。

we-found-that-users-with-any-experience-.origin:
We found that users with any experience playing an individual or team sport perform 11.9% better than
				those without such experience on average. Sports requiring a high degree of hand-eye coordination, such as Badminton, Tennis, and Golf,
				appear to have the highest positive effect on Beat Saber performance.
we-found-that-users-with-any-experience-.translated: 我们发现有任何个人或团队运动经验的用户平均表现比没有这种经验的用户好11.9%。像羽毛球、网球和高尔夫这样需要高度手眼协调能力的运动似乎对节奏光剑游戏的表现有最积极的影响。

warming-up-and-being-healthy-generally-i.origin: Warming up and being healthy generally improves performance in the game.
warming-up-and-being-healthy-generally-i.translated: 热身和保持健康通常会提高游戏表现。

unexpected-correlations-with-performance.translated: 与表现的意外相关因素

having-experience-with-rhythm-games-othe.origin:
Having experience with rhythm games other than Beat Saber has a slight negative effect
				on Beat Saber performance.
having-experience-with-rhythm-games-othe.translated: 参与过除了Beat Saber以外的其他音乐游戏会对Beat Saber的表现产生轻微的负面影响。

also-experience-with-musical-instruments.origin:
Also experience with musical instruments or dancing has a slight negative effect on Beat Saber performance.
				Beat Saber in fact is more like an athletic sport than a typical rhythm game.
also-experience-with-musical-instruments.translated: 此外，对乐器或舞蹈有经验也会对Beat Saber的表现产生轻微的负面影响。实际上，Beat Saber更像是一项体育运动，而不是传统的节奏游戏。

windows-10-users-outperform-windows-11-u.origin:
Windows 10 users outperform Windows 11 users by an average of 10.2%. A possible explanation for this
				may be that those who primarily use their PC for gaming may prefer Windows 10.
windows-10-users-outperform-windows-11-u.translated: 相比于Windows 11用户，Windows 10用户的表现平均超过10.2%。可能的解释是主要用于游戏的PC用户更喜欢使用Windows 10。

in-general-less-clothing-appears-to-corr.origin:
In general, less clothing appears to correlate with better performance, with fewer garments on the upper body,
				lower body, and feet all being associated with better average scores. This could be explained by the fact that clothing may serve to
				limit range of motion, or to reduce heat dissipation.
in-general-less-clothing-appears-to-corr.translated: 一般而言，穿得较少与较好的表现呈相关性，上身、下身和脚上的衣物越少，与更好的平均分数相关。这可能是因为衣物可能限制了动作范围，或减少了热量散发。

self-identified-conservatives-outperform.origin:
Self-identified conservatives outperform self-identified liberals by an average of 20.8%. This
				trend is particularly significant as it runs contrary to the finding that younger players generally perform better ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
self-identified-conservatives-outperform.translated: 自我认同为保守派的人平均表现比自我认同为自由派的人好出20.8%。这一趋势尤为重要，因为它与一般情况下年轻玩家表现更好的发现相矛盾 ¯\_(ツ)_/¯

thanks-to-everyone-who-took-part-in-the-.origin: Thanks to everyone who took part in the survey! Your responses provided insights on things we always wondered about.
thanks-to-everyone-who-took-part-in-the-.translated: 感谢参与调查的每个人！你们的回答为我们提供了我们一直想知道的见解。
